rows.label: qst610103_msg0001
rows.name:
So Eric's got you looking for
the timber thieves, has he?

rows.label: qst610103_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, he is the kind of guy to
take that sort of thing personally.
Makes sense, though.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0003
rows.name:
The Divine Beasts grow these staggering
trees, and you don't want all that effort
to go to waste or be taken in vain.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, I can at least tell you
all I know about the thief.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0005
rows.name:
It won't take long - because
I know absolutely nothing!

rows.label: qst610103_msg0006
rows.name:
Haha! Ahh, the look on
your face was priceless.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0007
rows.name:
Sorry, but the stuff was stolen while
the site was closed for the day.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0008
rows.name:
So nobody was here to see
anything. You might have a
tough time finding any witnesses.

rows.label: qst610103_msg0009
rows.name:
But, hey, that's not a reason to give
up. Keep asking. You never know who'll
give you a push in the right direction.
